name: A Harlem Shake vs Gangnam Jetpack Flying Shooting - Full version
name_original: A Harlem Shake vs Gangnam Jetpack Flying Shooting - Full version
description:
Oh SNAP! Harlem with a Jetpack vs Gangnam in aeroplanes!
Does it get any crazier than that!?

We didn't think so! Jump in and jetpack your way to Harlem glory as you blast your way past the Gangnam planes.

With classic jetpack action fly, shoot and collect as you battle in the ultimate dance scene.

Massive bass beats keep the action flowing in this crazy game that is fun for all the family.
